PrecisAuthority to amend the SELKIRK FIRST NATION SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to empower the first nation to enact laws relating to the implementation of measures made pursuant to any taxation agreement with the Minister of Finance and provide it with a GST refund paid by its government when performing its functions, effective November 1, 2000.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to amend the SELKIRK FIRST NATION SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to
empower the first nation to enact laws relating to the implementation of
measures made pursuant to any taxation agreement with the Minister of
Finance and provide it with a GST refund paid by its government when
performing its functions, effective November 1, 2000.
